## Root Cause Analysis Summary

**Root Cause Service**: `ts-ui-dashboard`

**Evidence**:
1. All 22 error traces show timeouts (20 seconds) on travel plan endpoints (`quickest`, `minStation`, `cheapest`)
2. Trace analysis reveals `ts-ui-dashboard` takes 20 seconds while its child `ts-travel-plan-service` completes in only 190ms
3. In normal conditions, both services take ~595ms, indicating the issue is specific to `ts-ui-dashboard` during the incident
4. `ts-ui-dashboard` metrics show healthy CPU and memory, ruling out resource exhaustion

**Fault Propagation Path**:
